<br />            
<span class="author"><a href="lane-ernest/1939/dawn-dusk/index.htm" class="small">E.H. Lane</a></span>            
(1868-1954) &lt;5<br />            
Australian Communist journalist, brother of Utopian William Lane.            
<br />            
<br />            
<span class="author"><a href="braunthal/index.htm">Julius Braunthal</a></span>            
(1891-1972) &lt;5<br />            
Austrian-born historian, journal editor, and political activist. He was the 
first Secretary General of refounded Socialist International from 1951-1956.</td></tr>            
            
