<br />            
<br />             
<span class="author"><a href="ilyenkov/index.htm" class="small">Evald Ilyenkov</a></span>            
(1924-1979) 5+ <img class="auto" src="images/red-star.jpg" alt="*" width="11" height="10" /><br />            
Soviet philosopher. Charted the materialist development of Hegel's dialectics. Wrote extensively on dialectics, the Metaphysics of Positivism, and The Dialectics of the Abstract and Concrete in Marx's Capital.            
<br />            
[<a class="biog" href="../glossary/people/i/l.htm#ilyenkov-evald">Biography</a>]            
