<h4><a href="../history/france/may-1968/index.htm" class="group" name="french-left">The French Left</a></h4>            
<span class="author"><a href="gaultier/index.htm" class="small-green">Jules de Gaultier</a></span>            
(1858-1942) &lt;5<br />            
French philosopher.            
<br />            
