<td class="note" valign="top">            
<span class="author"><a href="grant/index.htm" class="red">Ted Grant</a></span>            
(1913-2006) 100+ <img class="auto" src="images/red-star.jpg" alt="*" width="11" height="10" /><br />            
South African-born British Trotskyist, a founder and long-term leader in the &#8220;Militant Tendency&#8221; within the Labour Party until expelled from the Labour Party in 1983, and after.<br />            
[<a class="biog" href="grant/index.htm">Biography</a>]            
<br />            
<br />            
<span class="author"><a href="../history/etol/writers/hadden/index.htm" class="small-red">Peter Hadden</a></span>            
(1950-2010) 10+ <br />            
The leading theoretician of the Irish Militant group, later the Socialist Party, and the CWI.<br />            
[<a class="biog" href="../history/etol/writers/hadden/obits/irishtimes.html">Biography</a>]            
