(1946-2022) 20+<br />
U.S. Marxist urban theorist and historian. He wrote several influental books such as <em>City of Quartz</em> (1990), <em>Late Victorian Holocausts</em> (2001) and <em>Planet of Slums</em> (2006). He defined himself as international socialist and "Marxist-Environmentalist".
