<span class="author"><a href="hu-yaobang/index.htm">Hu Yaobang</a></span>            
(1915-1989)	&lt; 5<br />            
Chairman of the Chinese Communist Party from 1981 to 1982, and General Secretary 
from 1982 to 1987. Hu was an ally of Deng Xiaoping, and favored moving China and 
the CCP away from Mao-era policies.<br />            
<br />            
