<span class="author"><a href="haywood-b/index.htm" class="red">Bill Haywood</a></span>            
(1869-1928) &lt;5<br />            
Miner, leader of the I.W.W., socialist and syndicalist.<br />            
[<a class="biog" href="../glossary/people/h/a.htm#haywood-bill">Biography</a>]             
