<td width="50%" class="note" valign="top" colspan="2">            
<img src="../glossary/people/z/pics/zetkin.jpg" alt="Clara Zetkin" hspace="10" vspace="2" border="1" align="right" height="100" />            
<p class="fst"><br />&#8220;<a href="zetkin/1896/10/women.htm" class="cite">There is a women&#8217;s question for the women of the proletariat, the bourgeoisie, the intelligentsia and the Upper Ten Thousand. It assumes a different form according to the class situation of each one of these strata.</a>&#8221; [Clara Zetkin]</p>            
