[<a class="biography" href="../glossary/people/b/e.htm#begum-rokeya">Full Biography</a>]            
<br />            
<br />           
<span class="author"><a href="gandhy/index.htm" class="small-red">Anuradha Gandhy</a></span>        
(1954-2008) &lt;5<br />           
Member of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of India (Maoist). She directed her party's work among women, and was a leader in the trade union, and dalit and adivasi rights movements in Jharkand and Maharastra.            
