<br />
<br />
<span class="author"><a href="../archive/jozsef/index.htm" class="small">Attila J&oacute;zsef</a></span>            
(1905-1937)<br />            
Prominent Hungarian revolutionary poet. He was involved in various Communist groups throughout his life and wrote about Freudian-Marxism.
