<h4><a name="philosophy"> </a>            
<a href="../reference/subject/philosophy/index.htm">Philosophy</a></h4>            
The Value_of_Knowledge archive includes classic works by over 140 writers from the Copernican Revolution up to the present time, centred on problems in the epistemology, the theory of knowledge.<br /> <br />            
